够的资金来推动发展中国家脱碳至关重要。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.mckinsey.com/capabilities/sustainability/our-insights/solving-the-climate-finance-equation-for-developing-countries</guid></item><item><title>为什么组织需要首席运营官？</title><link>https://www.mckinsey.com/featured-insights/mckinsey-explainers/why-do-organizations-have-coos</link><description>运营主管是面向外部的首席执行官的制衡者，负责建立组织弹性和员工授权。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.mckinsey.com/featured-insights/mckinsey-explainers/why-do-organizations-have-coos</guid></item><item><title>与南·兰索霍夫 (Nan Ransohoff) 一起对从世界中消除碳这一棘手问题进行前瞻性思考</title><link>https://www.mckinsey.com/mgi/forward-thinking/forward-thinking-on-the-tricky-business-of-removing-carbon-from-our-world-with-nan-ransohoff</link><description>一家领先的碳减排投资做市商认为，应对气候变化必须迅速完成，但问题是可以解决的。悲观的想法已经走得太远了。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.mckinsey.com/mgi/forward-thinking/forward-thinking-on-the-tricky-business-of-removing-carbon-from-our-world-with-nan-ransohoff</guid></item><item><title>不确定性下的电网规划：能源转型投资</title><link>https://www.mckinsey.com/industries/electric-power-and-natural-gas/our-insights/grid-planning-under-uncertainty-investing-for-the-energy-transition</link><description>面对气候和转型风险，更新的规划范式可以帮助电网运营商应对不断变化的挑战，并确保电网的弹性和承受能力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.mckinsey.com/industries/electric-power-and-natural-gas/our-insights/grid-planning-under-uncertainty-investing-for-the-energy-transition</guid></item><item><title>“零”消费者的出现</title><link>https://www.mckinsey.com/featured-insights/future-of-asia/videos/the-emergence-of-the-zero-consumer</link><description>过去十年，零售业格局发生了怎样的变化？麦肯锡全球零售部门高级合伙人兼领导者 Dymfke Kuijpers 讨论了企业领导者应关注的最新趋势。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.mckinsey.com/featured-insights/future-of-asia/videos/the-emergence-of-the-zero-consumer</guid></item><item><title>充分发挥生成式人工智能在银行业的价值</title><link>https://www.mckinsey.com/industries/financial-services/our-insights/capturing-the-full-value-of-generative-ai-in-banking</link><description>设置 gen AI 飞行员很容易；扩展它们以获取物质价值是很困难的。成功的秘诀正在显现。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.mckinsey.com/industries/financial-services/our-insights/capturing-the-full-value-of-generative-ai-in-banking</guid></item><item><title>多样性更重要：整体影响力的案例</title><link>https://www.mckinsey.com/featured-insights/diversity-and-inclusion/diversity-matters-even-more-the-case-for-holistic-impact</link><description>尽管商业环境瞬息万变，但多元化、公平和包容性 (DEI) 的商业案例不仅成立，而且变得更加强大。在我们的研究中，我们继续探索多样性和整体影响之间的联系。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.mckinsey.com/featured-insights/diversity-and-inclusion/diversity-matters-even-more-the-case-for-holistic-impact</guid></item></channel></rss>